PrecisAmendments to the WORK FORCE ADJUSTMENT DIRECTIVE, 1996 that will affect employees represented by the Public Service Alliance of Canada and the Social Science Employees Association in the same way as other employees whose bargaining agents have negotiated a number of changes to the Directive respecting the transfer of work to the private sector.
Attachments
precis:
Amendments to the WORK FORCE ADJUSTMENT DIRECTIVE, 1996 that will affect
employees represented by the Public Service Alliance of Canada and the
Social Science Employees Association in the same way as other employees
whose bargaining agents have negotiated a number of changes to the
Directive respecting the transfer of work to the private sector.
